OL,3,CNottingham man jailed for threatening
OL,4,Cpeople with scissors
OL,6,FA man from has been jailed for
OL,7,Feighteen months for chasing people
OL,8,Fwith a pair of scissors and
OL,9,Fthreatening them with a padlock in the
OL,10,Fcity centre.
OL,12,FSam Sharpe, aged 27, brandished a pair
OL,13,Fof scissors after an argument with
OL,14,Fanother man.
OL,16,FSharpe then proceeded to charge at him
OL,17,Fwhile making multiple slashing motions
OL,18,Fthrough the air.
