OL,4,Cpeople with scissors
OL,6,FThis threatening behaviour carried on
OL,7,Ffor several minutes, while Sharpe
OL,8,Fcontinued to chase the man up and down
OL,9,Fthe road before leaving the scene.
OL,11,Fsays it was already looking for Sharpe
OL,12,Fin connection with a separate violent
OL,13,Fincident a few weeks earlier.
OL,15,FIn that incident, Sharpe walked into a
OL,16,FSainsbury's in Derby Road, Lenton and
OL,17,Fmade numerous threats to damage the
OL,18,Fshop and assault the people inside.
