OL,6,FSharpe then squared up to one staff
OL,7,Fmember and pushed a padlock he was
OL,8,Fcarrying against their forehead, while
OL,9,Fthreatening to hurt them with it.
OL,11,FThe victim suffered no injuries during
OL,12,Fthe incident.
OL,14,FAfter Nottinghamshire Police caught up
OL,15,Fwith Sharpe, he was charged with
OL,16,Fthreatening a person with a sharply
OL,17,Fpointed article in a public place and
OL,18,Fassault by beating.
