OL,6,FSharpe, of no fixed address, pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to both of these charges and
OL,8,Fwas sentenced at to eighteen months in
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Paul Crofts, of
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "The
OL,13,Fkind of violent behaviour demonstrated
OL,14,Fby Sharpe during both these incidents
OL,15,Fhas absolutely no place within our
OL,16,Fcommunities and will not be tolerated."
