OL,6,F"By choosing to arm himself with a
OL,7,Fweapon, and then chase after another
OL,8,Fperson with it, he knowingly created
OL,9,Fwhat must have been a very scary
OL,10,Fsituation for the other people in
OL,11,Fattendance."
OL,13,F"Fortunately, his actions didn't lead
OL,14,Fto anyone sustaining any injuries, but
OL,15,Fthis was still a very serious and
OL,16,Fdangerous offence."
