OL,6,F"Likewise, nobody was ultimately hurt
OL,7,Fwhen he was involved in another
OL,8,Fviolent incident ` this time holding
OL,9,Fanother potential weapon in his hand,
OL,10,Fin the form of a padlock."
OL,12,F"This level of violent intent is
OL,13,Fcompletely unacceptable, so we're
OL,14,Fpleased to see Sharpe has now been
OL,15,Flocked up for his behaviour."
